description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Plezier purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 189, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 3 for East, Box for South, and Box for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70633-13444-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [189 Votes, Top 5% Score]
